nodes.text: VibroSword Squadron was a starfighter squadron that was composed of Eta-5 interceptors. Syal Antilles, under the alias of Lysa Dunter, was part of the squadron, and was known as "V-Sword Seven." A Mon Calamari, serving as V-Sword Ten, flew as her wingmate. The unit participated in Operation Roundabout and was stationed aboard the battle carrier Dodonna.
